Package: mrclust
Type: Package
Title: Identifying clustered heterogeneity in Mendelian randomization analyses
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Neal Foley
Maintainer: The package maintainer <christopher.foley@mrc-bsu.cam.ac.uk>
Description: Performs likelihood based clustering on univariate observations with known uncertainty (via standard error data), whilst accounting for possible null and junk componenets in the sample.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: ggplot2, RColorBrewer, mclust, data.table, MendelianRandomization
